so raised for \"artificial\" de novo DNA synthesis\nprocesses of SARS-CoV2 spike genomes with no associated natural\nproofreading/selection, possibly including vaccine preparations.\n  Finally, a metric based on the ratio between prematurely stopped and \"normal\"\ngenomes is proposed as a potential host-independent variant-watching tool, able\nto classify the infectivity of new spike mutations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 May 2021 00:45:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 07:49:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-08"}
