ionic core-shell nanoparticles with low-fouling\nadsorption. This engineered multifunctional approach may provide therapeutic\npotential for the treatment of currently incurable ovarian cancer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 May 2021 09:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-24"}
